 but I picked up the phone, you know, shoot your shot.

41
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:56,220
 And I was like, hey, if I was gonna use that plane,

42
00:01:56,220 --> 00:01:58,580
 what would it cost or how much would it charge?

43
00:01:58,580 --> 00:02:00,860
 And I actually knew the pilot too.

44
