00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:53,320
 And so I couldn't see anything around me.

65
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,860
 You're looking outside of the passenger window

66
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:56,820
 and it storms everywhere.

67
00:02:56,820 --> 00:03:01,520
 And if all of that wasn't bad enough, I also knew the pilot.

68
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,260
 Now, here's why that's a problem

69
00:03:03,260 --> 00:03:05,000
 you probably have never thought about.

70
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,780
 There are certain professions that when they interact

71
